    "• GAOKAO-Bench (Zhang et al, 2023k).",
    "The GAOKAO-Bench dataset incorporates 2,811 directives in Chinese, sourced exclusively from meticulously crafted authentic questions found in Gaokao.",
    "Comprising a spectrum of 10 subjects-ranging from the Chinese to science and liberal arts mathematics, English, physics, chemistry, biology, geography, politics, and history-the dataset serves as a means to assess the holistic capacities of LLMs.",
    "These capacities encompass language understanding and logical deduction, as manifested in their responses to Gaokao queries.",
    "The evaluative content spans questions spanning the period from 2010 to 2022, encompassing 1,781 objective questions and 1,030 subjective questions derived from GaoKao."
